Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩三人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…您这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:05.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑…快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:12.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊  你们以为跑得掉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
